FSRI: Dimensions: 99.95 x 99.30 x 39.76 mm; with frame and grid

The laminate bubbled, then popped at about 1 minute causing a spike in mass data. There were intermittant candle-sized flames prior to ignition. Marked ignition began as a candle sized flame near center of sample, and remained steady for about 2.5 minutes until extinguishing at 7:42. The spark ignitor was reinserted, and reignition occurred at 9:30, and flames spread across the entire sample surface and sustained until end of test.
